Package nz.ac.vuw.ecs.swen225.gp30.maze.tile

Class Tile

  • java.lang.Object
    • nz.ac.vuw.ecs.swen225.gp30.maze.tile.Tile
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    GameObject
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ExitLockTile, ExitTile, FreeTile, InfoTile, KeyTile, LockedDoorTile, TreasureTile, WallTile
    public abstract class Tile
extends java.lang.Object
implements GameObject
    The Tile class abstracts tiles within the maze. Provides access to the x and y position of the tile. Provides functionality which should be implemented by subclasses: - check validity of movement. - check whether the tile contains an actor. - game logic for adding and removing an actor. - image name for display.
    Author:
    campliosca 300489876
